https://www.you​tube.com/watch?​v=oSQLKk_Hgg0 http://nsgl.gso​.uri.edu/oresu/​oresuv15006_021​.html (Oregon's Working Waterfront Tour Series) https://itunes.​apple.com/us/ap​p/oregons-​working-​waterfronts/id9​62972556?mt=8 (Related app: iTunes) https://play.go​ogle.com/store/​apps/details?id​=edu.oregonstat​e.cass.WorkingW​aterfrontsMobil​e (Related app: Google Play)

A video showing how port biologists from the Oregon Fish and Wildlife Department monitor fish landings, take samples and measurements, and look for internal tags to make decisions about sustainable harvests.
